{"tid":652321,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分手後有冇發現不一樣既自己？","createTime":"2018-05-03T18:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T18:59:07.000Z","uid":37282,"like":31,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"15184ae05e04780a8aa6b0e2ce6e66237423013a","tid":652321,"uid":37282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T18:30:22.000Z","msg":"有冇人拍拖果陣會比好多限制自己<br />\n例如盡量避免同異性傾計<br />\n就連本身係朋友都盡量唔見面<br />\n覺得應該安守本份 <br />\n廢事另一半亂諗<br />\n<br />\n由中學拍拖到long d 都冇偷食過<br />\n仲日日FaceTime 傾計<br />\n盡量令另一半放心<br />\n好努力咁維繫<br />\n但到返香港先發覺原來好多野都已經磨合唔到<br />\n例如大家既價值觀咁<br />\n<br />\n分左手之後發覺本身朋友唔多<br />\n想開始擴闊自己圈子<br />\n又發覺自己原來好多包袱同顧慮<br />\n後來慢慢開始放底自己既包袱<br />\n每一日都享受單身<br />\n做自己想做既野而又唔洗同人交代<br />\n同朋友玩到癲晒 果種自由自在既感覺好舒服<br />\n<br />\n可惜有時又希望有個伴可以一齊長大<br />\n見證大家成長進步到一齊組織家庭<br />\n但又好似真係唔想再諗拍拖既野住<br />\n唉 究竟有冇人明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c75cf902e3dfacf32dca2ca6d215e5332af568f","tid":652321,"uid":37282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T18:33:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e8a96e0d3faabef2423f7d747a6445fc33f7e6b","tid":652321,"uid":79389,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T18:35:19.000Z","msg":"最尾果段same here<br />\n好驚再面對分手 再重新開始<br />\n但又好想有個人一齊成長 互相分享<br />\n<br />\n有代價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a09f8102ec6bb8754bb430ceb07bc149232e571e","tid":652321,"uid":15886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T18:37:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a23ce8689d35939fd3c9e3a80161873d594c92","tid":652321,"uid":37282,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2e8a96e0d3faabef2423f7d747a6445fc33f7e6b","tid":652321,"uid":79389,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T18:35:19.00